        <h2>42. Sequence: Microservice Orchestration</h2>
        <p class="description">Complex multi-service flow with parallel calls and error handling.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sample-content">
        <div class="source-panel">
          <h3>Mermaid Source</h3>
          <pre><code>sequenceDiagram
  participant G as Gateway
  participant A as Auth
  participant U as Users
  participant O as Orders
  participant N as Notify
  G-&gt;&gt;A: Validate token
  A--&gt;&gt;G: Valid
  par Fetch data
    G-&gt;&gt;U: Get user
    U--&gt;&gt;G: User data
  and
    G-&gt;&gt;O: Get orders
    O--&gt;&gt;G: Order list
  end
  G-&gt;&gt;N: Send notification
  N--&gt;&gt;G: Queued
  Note over G: Aggregate response</code></pre>
          
        </div>
